  "system": {
    "description": "<p>When you make an <strong>Attack</strong> with a <strong>Light</strong> <strong>Weapon</strong>, you can spend <strong>1 SP</strong> to force the target to make a <strong>Physical</strong> <strong>Save</strong> against your <strong>Save DC</strong>.</p><p>Make an <strong>Attack Check </strong>against the target, and it makes a <strong>Physical Save </strong>against your <strong>Save DC</strong>. </p><p><strong>Attack Hit: </strong>It takes your Weapon damage.</p><p><strong>Save Failure: </strong>Until the end of your next turn, it suffers 1 effect of your choice:</p><ul><li><strong>Exposed </strong>(Attack Checks against it have ADV)</li><li><strong>Deafened </strong>(it cannot hear)</li><li><strong>Hindered </strong>(it has DisADV on Attack Checks)</li><li><strong>Slowed 2</strong> (every 1 Space it moves costs an extra 2 Space of movement)</li></ul><p>A target can’t be affected by the same option more than once at a time. </p><p></p><p><em><strong>System Tip: </strong>You can add Weapon to use together with that Feature. Select it on <strong>Details </strong>Tab of that <strong>Feature</strong>.</em></p>",
